sequenceDiagram
            actor Admin
            participant View as Halaman Dasbor
            participant Controller as ClusteringController
            participant Service as KMeansService
            participant Database as SQLite Database
            
            Admin->>View: Buka halaman hasil clustering
            View->>Controller: Request Data Cluster()
            Controller->>Service: runClustering()
            Service->>Database: Ambil Histori Transaksi (30 Hari)
            Database-->>Service: Kembalikan Data Penjualan
            Service->>Service: Hitung Frekuensi & Kuantitas
            Service->>Service: Tentukan Centroid (K=3)
            Service->>Service: Hitung Jarak Euclidean (Iterasi)
            Service->>Database: Simpan Hasil Klasifikasi (High/Mid/Low)
            Service-->>Controller: Return Array(Cluster_Data)
            Controller-->>View: Render Grafik K-Means
            View-->>Admin: Tampilkan Rekomendasi Restock